[
  {
    "startTime": 15.26,
    "endTime": 18.259,
    "text": "Sometimes I go browsing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.26,
    "endTime": 20.26,
    "text": "[through] a very old magazine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.26,
    "endTime": 23.26,
    "text": "I found this observation test"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.26,
    "endTime": 26.26,
    "text": "about the story of the ark."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.26,
    "endTime": 29.26,
    "text": "And the artist that drew this observation test"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.26,
    "endTime": 31.26,
    "text": "did some errors, had some mistakes --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.26,
    "endTime": 33.260000000000005,
    "text": "there are more or less 12 mistakes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.26,
    "endTime": 35.26,
    "text": "Some of them are very easy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.26,
    "endTime": 38.26,
    "text": "There is a funnel, an aerial part,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.26,
    "endTime": 40.26,
    "text": "a lamp and clockwork key on the ark."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.26,
    "endTime": 43.26,
    "text": "Some of them are about the animals, the number."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.26,
    "endTime": 46.26,
    "text": "But there is a much more fundamental mistake"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.26,
    "endTime": 49.26,
    "text": "in the overall story of the ark"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.26,
    "endTime": 51.26,
    "text": "that's not reported here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.26,
    "endTime": 54.26,
    "text": "And this problem is: where are the plants?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.26,
    "endTime": 56.26,
    "text": "So now we have God"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.26,
    "endTime": 59.26,
    "text": "that is going to submerge Earth permanently"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.26,
    "endTime": 62.26,
    "text": "or at least for a very long period,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.26,
    "endTime": 65.259,
    "text": "and no one is taking care of plants."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.26,
    "endTime": 67.26,
    "text": "Noah needed to take two of every kind of bird,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.26,
    "endTime": 69.26,
    "text": "of every kind of animal,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.26,
    "endTime": 71.26,
    "text": "of every kind of creature that moves,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.26,
    "endTime": 74.26,
    "text": "but no mention about plants."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.26,
    "endTime": 76.26,
    "text": "Why?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.26,
    "endTime": 78.26,
    "text": "In another part of the same story,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.26,
    "endTime": 80.26,
    "text": "all the living creatures"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.26,
    "endTime": 82.26,
    "text": "are just the living creatures"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.26,
    "endTime": 84.26,
    "text": "that came out from the ark,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.26,
    "endTime": 87.26,
    "text": "so birds, livestock and wild animals."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.26,
    "endTime": 89.26,
    "text": "Plants are not living creatures --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.26,
    "endTime": 91.26,
    "text": "this is the point."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.26,
    "endTime": 93.26,
    "text": "That is a point that is not"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.26,
    "endTime": 95.26,
    "text": "coming out from the Bible,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.26,
    "endTime": 97.26,
    "text": "but it's something that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.26,
    "endTime": 100.26,
    "text": "really accompanied humanity."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.26,
    "endTime": 103.26,
    "text": "Let's have a look at this nice code"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.26,
    "endTime": 106.26,
    "text": "that is coming from a Renaissance book."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.26,
    "endTime": 108.26,
    "text": "Here we have the description"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.26,
    "endTime": 110.26,
    "text": "of the order of nature."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.26,
    "endTime": 113.26,
    "text": "It's a nice description because it's starting from left --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.26,
    "endTime": 115.26,
    "text": "you have the stones --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.26,
    "endTime": 117.26,
    "text": "immediately after the stones, the plants"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.26,
    "endTime": 120.26,
    "text": "that are just able to live."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.26,
    "endTime": 123.26,
    "text": "We have the animals that are able to live and to sense,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.26,
    "endTime": 125.26,
    "text": "and on the top of the pyramid,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.26,
    "endTime": 127.26,
    "text": "there is the man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.26,
    "endTime": 129.25900000000001,
    "text": "This is not the common man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.259,
    "endTime": 132.26,
    "text": "The \"Homo studiosus\" -- the studying man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.26,
    "endTime": 135.26,
    "text": "This is quite comforting"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.26,
    "endTime": 138.26,
    "text": "for people like me -- I'm a professor --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.26,
    "endTime": 141.26,
    "text": "this to be over there on the top of creation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.26,
    "endTime": 144.26,
    "text": "But it's something completely wrong."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.26,
    "endTime": 147.26,
    "text": "You know very well about professors."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.26,
    "endTime": 150.26,
    "text": "But it's also wrong about plants,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.26,
    "endTime": 152.26,
    "text": "because plants are not just able to live;"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.26,
    "endTime": 154.26,
    "text": "they are able to sense."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.26,
    "endTime": 156.26,
    "text": "They are much more sophisticated"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.26,
    "endTime": 158.26,
    "text": "in sensing than animals."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.26,
    "endTime": 160.26,
    "text": "Just to give you an example,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.26,
    "endTime": 162.26,
    "text": "every single root apex"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.26,
    "endTime": 165.26,
    "text": "is able to detect and to monitor"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.26,
    "endTime": 167.26,
    "text": "concurrently and continuously"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.26,
    "endTime": 169.26,
    "text": "at least 15 different chemical"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.26,
    "endTime": 172.26,
    "text": "and physical parameters."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.26,
    "endTime": 175.26,
    "text": "And they also are able to show and to exhibit"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.26,
    "endTime": 178.26,
    "text": "such a wonderful and complex behavior"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.26,
    "endTime": 181.26,
    "text": "that can be described just with the term of intelligence."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.26,
    "endTime": 184.26,
    "text": "Well, but this is something --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.26,
    "endTime": 186.26,
    "text": "this underestimation of plants is something"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.26,
    "endTime": 189.26,
    "text": "that is always with us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.26,
    "endTime": 192.26,
    "text": "Let's have a look at this short movie now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.26,
    "endTime": 194.26,
    "text": "We have David Attenborough."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.26,
    "endTime": 196.26,
    "text": "Now David Attenborough is really a plant lover;"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.26,
    "endTime": 199.26,
    "text": "he did some of the most beautiful movies"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.26,
    "endTime": 201.26,
    "text": "about plant behavior."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.26,
    "endTime": 203.26,
    "text": "Now, when he speaks about plants,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.26,
    "endTime": 205.26,
    "text": "everything is correct."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.26,
    "endTime": 207.26,
    "text": "When he speaks about animals,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.26,
    "endTime": 209.26,
    "text": "[he] tends to remove the fact"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.26,
    "endTime": 211.26,
    "text": "that plants exist."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.26,
    "endTime": 213.26,
    "text": "The blue whale,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.26,
    "endTime": 215.26,
    "text": "the biggest creature that exists on the planet --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.26,
    "endTime": 218.26,
    "text": "that is wrong, completely wrong."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.26,
    "endTime": 221.26,
    "text": "The blue whale, it's a dwarf"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.26,
    "endTime": 223.26,
    "text": "if compared with the real biggest creature"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.26,
    "endTime": 225.26,
    "text": "that exists on the planet --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.26,
    "endTime": 227.26,
    "text": "that is, this wonderful,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.26,
    "endTime": 231.26,
    "text": "magnificent Sequoiadendron giganteum."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.26,
    "endTime": 233.26,
    "text": "(Applause)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.26,
    "endTime": 236.26,
    "text": "And this is a living organism"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.26,
    "endTime": 239.26,
    "text": "that has a mass of at least 2,000 tons."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.26,
    "endTime": 241.26,
    "text": "Now, the story"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.26,
    "endTime": 244.26,
    "text": "that plants are some low-level organisms"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244.26,
    "endTime": 247.26,
    "text": "has been formalized"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.26,
    "endTime": 250.26,
    "text": "many times ago by Aristotle,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.26,
    "endTime": 252.26,
    "text": "that in \"De Anima\" --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.26,
    "endTime": 255.26,
    "text": "that is a very influential book for the Western civilization --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.26,
    "endTime": 258.26,
    "text": "wrote that the plants are on the edge"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.26,
    "endTime": 261.26,
    "text": "between living and not living."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.26,
    "endTime": 264.26,
    "text": "They have just a kind of very low-level soul."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.26,
    "endTime": 267.26,
    "text": "It's called the vegetative soul,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.26,
    "endTime": 270.26,
    "text": "because they lack movement,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 270.26,
    "endTime": 272.26,
    "text": "and so they don't need to sense."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.26,
    "endTime": 274.26,
    "text": "Let's see."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.26,
    "endTime": 277.26,
    "text": "Okay, some of the movements of the plants are very well-known."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.26,
    "endTime": 279.26,
    "text": "This is a very fast movement."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.26,
    "endTime": 282.26,
    "text": "This is a Dionaea, a Venus fly trap"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.26,
    "endTime": 284.26,
    "text": "hunting snails --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 284.26,
    "endTime": 286.26,
    "text": "sorry for the snail."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 286.26,
    "endTime": 289.26,
    "text": "This has been something that has been refused for centuries,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 289.26,
    "endTime": 292.26,
    "text": "despite the evidence."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 292.26,
    "endTime": 295.26,
    "text": "No one can say that the plants were able to eat an animal,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 295.26,
    "endTime": 298.26,
    "text": "because it was against the order of nature."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 298.26,
    "endTime": 300.26,
    "text": "But plants are also able"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 300.26,
    "endTime": 303.26,
    "text": "to show a lot of movement."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 303.26,
    "endTime": 306.26,
    "text": "Some of them are very well known, like the flowering."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306.26,
    "endTime": 309.26,
    "text": "It's just a question to use some techniques"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 309.26,
    "endTime": 311.26,
    "text": "like the time lapse."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 311.26,
    "endTime": 314.26,
    "text": "Some of them are much more sophisticated."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 314.26,
    "endTime": 316.26,
    "text": "Look at this young bean"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 316.26,
    "endTime": 319.26,
    "text": "that is moving to catch the light every time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 319.26,
    "endTime": 321.26,
    "text": "And it's really so graceful;"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 321.26,
    "endTime": 324.26,
    "text": "it's like a dancing angel."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 324.26,
    "endTime": 327.26,
    "text": "They are also able to play --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 327.26,
    "endTime": 329.26,
    "text": "they are really playing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 329.26,
    "endTime": 332.26,
    "text": "These are young sunflowers,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 332.26,
    "endTime": 334.26,
    "text": "and what they are doing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 334.26,
    "endTime": 336.26,
    "text": "cannot be described"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336.26,
    "endTime": 338.26,
    "text": "with any other terms than playing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 338.26,
    "endTime": 340.26,
    "text": "They are training themselves,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 340.26,
    "endTime": 342.26,
    "text": "as many young animals do,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 342.26,
    "endTime": 344.26,
    "text": "to the adult life"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 344.26,
    "endTime": 347.26,
    "text": "where they will be called to track the sun"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 347.26,
    "endTime": 349.26,
    "text": "all the day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 349.26,
    "endTime": 352.26,
    "text": "They are able to respond to gravity, of course,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 352.26,
    "endTime": 354.26,
    "text": "so the shoots are growing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 354.26,
    "endTime": 356.26,
    "text": "against the vector of gravity"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 356.26,
    "endTime": 359.26,
    "text": "and the roots toward the vector of gravity."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 359.26,
    "endTime": 362.26,
    "text": "But they are also able to sleep."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 362.26,
    "endTime": 364.26,
    "text": "This is one, Mimosa pudica."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 364.26,
    "endTime": 366.26,
    "text": "So during the night,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 366.26,
    "endTime": 368.26,
    "text": "they curl the leaves"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 368.26,
    "endTime": 370.26,
    "text": "and reduce the movement,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 370.26,
    "endTime": 372.26,
    "text": "and during the day, you have the opening of the leaves --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 372.26,
    "endTime": 374.26,
    "text": "there is much more movement."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 374.26,
    "endTime": 376.26,
    "text": "This is interesting"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 376.26,
    "endTime": 378.26,
    "text": "because this sleeping machinery,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 378.26,
    "endTime": 380.26,
    "text": "it's perfectly conserved."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 380.26,
    "endTime": 382.26,
    "text": "It's the same in plants, in insects"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 382.26,
    "endTime": 384.26,
    "text": "and in animals."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 384.26,
    "endTime": 387.26,
    "text": "And so if you need to study this sleeping problem,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 387.26,
    "endTime": 390.26,
    "text": "it's easy to study on plants, for example,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 390.26,
    "endTime": 392.26,
    "text": "than in animals"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 392.26,
    "endTime": 395.26,
    "text": "and it's much more easy even ethically."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 395.26,
    "endTime": 398.26,
    "text": "It's a kind of vegetarian"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 398.26,
    "endTime": 400.26,
    "text": "experimentation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 400.26,
    "endTime": 403.26,
    "text": "Plants are even able to communicate --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 403.26,
    "endTime": 405.26,
    "text": "they are extraordinary communicators."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 405.26,
    "endTime": 407.26,
    "text": "They communicate with other plants."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 407.26,
    "endTime": 410.26,
    "text": "They are able to distinguish kin and non-kin."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 410.26,
    "endTime": 412.26,
    "text": "They communicate"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 412.26,
    "endTime": 414.26,
    "text": "with plants of other species"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 414.26,
    "endTime": 416.26,
    "text": "and they communicate with animals"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 416.26,
    "endTime": 419.26,
    "text": "by producing chemical volatiles,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 419.26,
    "endTime": 421.26,
    "text": "for example, during the pollination."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 421.26,
    "endTime": 424.26,
    "text": "Now with the pollination, it's a very serious issue for plants,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 424.26,
    "endTime": 427.26,
    "text": "because they move the pollen from one flower to the other,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 427.26,
    "endTime": 429.26,
    "text": "yet they cannot move from one flower to the other."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 429.26,
    "endTime": 431.26,
    "text": "So they need a vector --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 431.26,
    "endTime": 433.26,
    "text": "and this vector,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 433.26,
    "endTime": 435.26,
    "text": "it's normally an animal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 435.26,
    "endTime": 437.26,
    "text": "Many insects"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 437.26,
    "endTime": 440.26,
    "text": "have been used by plants as vectors"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 440.26,
    "endTime": 442.26,
    "text": "for the transport of the pollination,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 442.26,
    "endTime": 445.26,
    "text": "but not just insects; even birds, reptiles,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 445.26,
    "endTime": 448.26,
    "text": "and mammals like bats rats"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 448.26,
    "endTime": 451.26,
    "text": "are normally used for the transportation of the pollen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 451.26,
    "endTime": 453.26,
    "text": "This is a serious business."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 453.26,
    "endTime": 456.26,
    "text": "We have the plants that are giving to the animals"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 456.26,
    "endTime": 459.26,
    "text": "a kind of sweet substance --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 459.26,
    "endTime": 461.26,
    "text": "very energizing --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 461.26,
    "endTime": 464.26,
    "text": "having in change this transportation of the pollen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 464.26,
    "endTime": 467.26,
    "text": "But some plants are manipulating animals,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 467.26,
    "endTime": 469.26,
    "text": "like in the case of orchids"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 469.26,
    "endTime": 471.26,
    "text": "that promise sex and nectar"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 471.26,
    "endTime": 473.26,
    "text": "and give in change nothing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 473.26,
    "endTime": 476.26,
    "text": "for the transportation of the pollen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 476.26,
    "endTime": 479.26,
    "text": "Now, there is a big problem"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 479.26,
    "endTime": 482.26,
    "text": "behind all this behavior that we have seen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 482.26,
    "endTime": 485.26,
    "text": "How is it possible to do this without a brain?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 485.26,
    "endTime": 488.26,
    "text": "We need to wait until 1880,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 488.26,
    "endTime": 490.26,
    "text": "when this big man,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 490.26,
    "endTime": 492.26,
    "text": "Charles Darwin,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 492.26,
    "endTime": 495.26,
    "text": "publishes a wonderful, astonishing book"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 495.26,
    "endTime": 498.26,
    "text": "that starts a revolution."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 498.26,
    "endTime": 501.26,
    "text": "The title is \"The Power of Movement in Plants.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 501.26,
    "endTime": 503.26,
    "text": "No one was allowed to speak about movement in plants"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 503.26,
    "endTime": 505.26,
    "text": "before Charles Darwin."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 505.26,
    "endTime": 507.26,
    "text": "In his book,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 507.26,
    "endTime": 509.26,
    "text": "assisted by his son, Francis --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 509.26,
    "endTime": 512.26,
    "text": "who was the first professor of plant physiology in the world, in Cambridge --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 512.26,
    "endTime": 515.26,
    "text": "they took into consideration every single movement"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 515.26,
    "endTime": 517.26,
    "text": "for 500 pages."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 517.26,
    "endTime": 520.26,
    "text": "And in the last paragraph of the book,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 520.26,
    "endTime": 522.26,
    "text": "it's a kind of stylistic mark,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 522.26,
    "endTime": 525.26,
    "text": "because normally Charles Darwin stored,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 525.26,
    "endTime": 527.26,
    "text": "in the last paragraph of a book,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 527.26,
    "endTime": 529.26,
    "text": "the most important message."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 529.26,
    "endTime": 531.26,
    "text": "He wrote that,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 531.26,
    "endTime": 533.26,
    "text": "\"It's hardly an exaggeration"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 533.26,
    "endTime": 536.26,
    "text": "to say that the tip of the radical"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 536.26,
    "endTime": 538.26,
    "text": "acts like the brain"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 538.26,
    "endTime": 540.26,
    "text": "of one of the lower animals.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 540.26,
    "endTime": 542.26,
    "text": "This is not a metaphor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 542.26,
    "endTime": 545.26,
    "text": "He wrote some very interesting letters to one of his friends"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 545.26,
    "endTime": 549.26,
    "text": "who was J.D. Hooker, or at that time, president of the Royal Society,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 549.26,
    "endTime": 552.26,
    "text": "so the maximum scientific authority in Britain"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 552.26,
    "endTime": 555.26,
    "text": "speaking about the brain in the plants."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 555.26,
    "endTime": 557.26,
    "text": "Now, this is a root apex"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 557.26,
    "endTime": 559.26,
    "text": "growing against a slope."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 559.26,
    "endTime": 562.26,
    "text": "So you can recognize this kind of movement,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 562.26,
    "endTime": 565.26,
    "text": "the same movement that worms, snakes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 565.26,
    "endTime": 567.26,
    "text": "and every animal"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 567.26,
    "endTime": 570.26,
    "text": "that are moving on the ground without legs"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 570.26,
    "endTime": 572.26,
    "text": "is able to display."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 572.26,
    "endTime": 574.26,
    "text": "And it's not an easy movement"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 574.26,
    "endTime": 577.26,
    "text": "because, to have this kind of movement,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 577.26,
    "endTime": 580.26,
    "text": "you need to move different regions of the root"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 580.26,
    "endTime": 582.26,
    "text": "and to synchronize these different regions"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 582.26,
    "endTime": 584.26,
    "text": "without having a brain."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 584.26,
    "endTime": 587.26,
    "text": "So we studied the root apex"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 587.26,
    "endTime": 589.26,
    "text": "and we found that there is a specific region"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 589.26,
    "endTime": 592.26,
    "text": "that is here, depicted in blue --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 592.26,
    "endTime": 594.26,
    "text": "that is called the \"transition zone.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 594.26,
    "endTime": 597.26,
    "text": "And this region, it's a very small region --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 597.26,
    "endTime": 600.26,
    "text": "it's less than one millimeter."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 600.26,
    "endTime": 602.26,
    "text": "And in this small region"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 602.26,
    "endTime": 604.26,
    "text": "you have the highest consumption"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 604.26,
    "endTime": 606.26,
    "text": "of oxygen in the plants"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 606.26,
    "endTime": 608.26,
    "text": "and more important,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 608.26,
    "endTime": 610.26,
    "text": "you have these kinds of signals here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 610.26,
    "endTime": 613.26,
    "text": "The signals that you are seeing here are action potential,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 613.26,
    "endTime": 615.26,
    "text": "are the same signals"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 615.26,
    "endTime": 618.26,
    "text": "that the neurons of my brain, of our brain,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 618.26,
    "endTime": 621.26,
    "text": "use to exchange information."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 621.26,
    "endTime": 624.26,
    "text": "Now we know that a root apex"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 624.26,
    "endTime": 626.26,
    "text": "has just a few hundred cells"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 626.26,
    "endTime": 628.26,
    "text": "that show this kind of feature,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 628.26,
    "endTime": 630.26,
    "text": "but we know how big"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 630.26,
    "endTime": 633.26,
    "text": "the root apparatus of a small plant, like a plant of rye."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 633.26,
    "endTime": 635.26,
    "text": "We have almost"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 635.26,
    "endTime": 637.26,
    "text": "14 million roots."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 637.26,
    "endTime": 640.26,
    "text": "We have 11 and a half million"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 640.26,
    "endTime": 642.26,
    "text": "root apex"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 642.26,
    "endTime": 645.26,
    "text": "and a total length of 600 or more kilometers"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 645.26,
    "endTime": 647.26,
    "text": "and a very high surface area."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 647.26,
    "endTime": 649.26,
    "text": "Now let's imagine"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 649.26,
    "endTime": 651.26,
    "text": "that each single root apex"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 651.26,
    "endTime": 654.26,
    "text": "is working in network with all the others."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 654.26,
    "endTime": 657.26,
    "text": "Here were have on the left, the Internet"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 657.26,
    "endTime": 660.26,
    "text": "and on the right, the root apparatus."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 660.26,
    "endTime": 662.26,
    "text": "They work in the same way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 662.26,
    "endTime": 664.26,
    "text": "They are a network"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 664.26,
    "endTime": 666.26,
    "text": "of small computing machines,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 666.26,
    "endTime": 668.26,
    "text": "working in networks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 668.26,
    "endTime": 670.26,
    "text": "And why are they so similar?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 670.26,
    "endTime": 672.26,
    "text": "Because they evolved"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 672.26,
    "endTime": 674.26,
    "text": "for the same reason:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 674.26,
    "endTime": 677.26,
    "text": "to survive predation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 677.26,
    "endTime": 679.26,
    "text": "They work in the same way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 679.26,
    "endTime": 682.26,
    "text": "So you can remove 90 percent of the root apparatus"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 682.26,
    "endTime": 684.26,
    "text": "and the plants [continue] to work."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 684.26,
    "endTime": 687.26,
    "text": "You can remove 90 percent of the Internet"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 687.26,
    "endTime": 690.26,
    "text": "and it is [continuing] to work."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 690.26,
    "endTime": 692.26,
    "text": "So, a suggestion"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 692.26,
    "endTime": 695.26,
    "text": "for the people working with networks:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 695.26,
    "endTime": 698.26,
    "text": "plants are able"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 698.26,
    "endTime": 700.26,
    "text": "to give you good suggestions"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 700.26,
    "endTime": 703.26,
    "text": "about how to evolve networks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 703.26,
    "endTime": 706.26,
    "text": "And another possibility"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 706.26,
    "endTime": 709.26,
    "text": "is a technological possibility."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 709.26,
    "endTime": 711.26,
    "text": "Let's imagine"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 711.26,
    "endTime": 713.26,
    "text": "that we can build robots"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 713.26,
    "endTime": 716.26,
    "text": "and robots that are inspired by plants."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 716.26,
    "endTime": 718.26,
    "text": "Until now,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 718.26,
    "endTime": 721.26,
    "text": "the man was inspired"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 721.26,
    "endTime": 723.26,
    "text": "just by man or the animals"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 723.26,
    "endTime": 725.26,
    "text": "in producing a robot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 725.26,
    "endTime": 728.26,
    "text": "We have the animaloid --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 728.26,
    "endTime": 730.26,
    "text": "and the normal robots inspired by animals,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 730.26,
    "endTime": 732.26,
    "text": "insectoid, so on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 732.26,
    "endTime": 734.26,
    "text": "We have the androids"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 734.26,
    "endTime": 737.26,
    "text": "that are inspired by man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 737.26,
    "endTime": 740.26,
    "text": "But why have we not any plantoid?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 740.26,
    "endTime": 742.26,
    "text": "Well, if you want to fly,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 742.26,
    "endTime": 744.26,
    "text": "it's good that you look at birds --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 744.26,
    "endTime": 746.26,
    "text": "to be inspired by birds."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 746.26,
    "endTime": 749.26,
    "text": "But if you want to explore soils,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 749.26,
    "endTime": 752.26,
    "text": "or if you want to colonize"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 752.26,
    "endTime": 754.26,
    "text": "new territory,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 754.26,
    "endTime": 757.26,
    "text": "to best thing that you can do is to be inspired by plants"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 757.26,
    "endTime": 760.26,
    "text": "that are masters in doing this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 760.26,
    "endTime": 762.26,
    "text": "We have another possibility"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 762.26,
    "endTime": 764.26,
    "text": "we are working [on] in our lab,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 764.26,
    "endTime": 766.26,
    "text": "[which] is to build hybrids."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 766.26,
    "endTime": 769.26,
    "text": "It's much more easy to build hybrids."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 769.26,
    "endTime": 771.26,
    "text": "Hybrid means it's something"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 771.26,
    "endTime": 774.26,
    "text": "that's half living and half machine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 774.26,
    "endTime": 776.26,
    "text": "It's much more easy to work with plants"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 776.26,
    "endTime": 778.26,
    "text": "than with animals."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 778.26,
    "endTime": 780.26,
    "text": "They have computing power,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 780.26,
    "endTime": 782.26,
    "text": "they have electrical signals."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 782.26,
    "endTime": 785.26,
    "text": "The connection with the machine is much more easy,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 785.26,
    "endTime": 789.26,
    "text": "much more even ethically possible."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 790.26,
    "endTime": 792.26,
    "text": "And these are three possibilities"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 792.26,
    "endTime": 795.26,
    "text": "that we are working on"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 795.26,
    "endTime": 797.26,
    "text": "to build hybrids,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 797.26,
    "endTime": 799.26,
    "text": "driven by algae"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 799.26,
    "endTime": 802.26,
    "text": "or by the leaves at the end,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 802.26,
    "endTime": 804.26,
    "text": "by the most, most powerful parts of the plants,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 804.26,
    "endTime": 806.26,
    "text": "by the roots."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 806.26,
    "endTime": 808.26,
    "text": "Well, thank you for your attention."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 808.26,
    "endTime": 811.26,
    "text": "And before I finish,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 811.26,
    "endTime": 814.26,
    "text": "I would like to reassure that no snails were harmed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 814.26,
    "endTime": 816.26,
    "text": "in making this presentation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 816.26,
    "endTime": 818.26,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 818.26,
    "endTime": 823.26,
    "text": "(Applause)"
  }
]